From 3a3afee1b71f01cb26f77c7cf142a6cb48d9bec6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ramesh Mandal <ramesh@6epixels.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 03:30:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(float): complete compact chat experience, fixed layout

Root cause of the broken layout: the popup document kept the default
body margin, so content was 100vh+16px, the window itself scrolled, the
identity header scrolled out of view and a dead gap appeared below the
composer. html/body/#root now reset to full height with overflow hidden.

The float is now a true miniature of the main chat:
- identity header: avatar/photo, name (alias-aware), presence dot,
  typing state, member count for communities, Live/Offline pill
- typing indicator bubble (three-dot), typing relayed FROM the float
  (throttled, accepted connections only)
- timestamps on bubbles, clickable link cards (open in new tab),
  community author names/colors
- emoji picker and share-tab in the composer
- iMessage spring animations respecting the Settings toggle
- graceful empty state when no conversation exists yet
